        "summary_hpMNBU": {
          "type": "summary",
          "settings": {
            "summary_text": "<p><strong>Summary:</strong> You can now whiten at home without a $600 in-chair bill or messy guesswork. The Elaren routine pairs a Purple Mouthwash for instant brightness, enamel-safe Whitening Strips for deeper results, and a hands-free LED Device that brightens your whole smile at once. Alcohol-free and gentle on your enamel, backed by a 30-day money-back guarantee. Keep reading for the ten reasons it is worth switching.</p>"
          }
        },
